# 行尾规范化:默认 LF,Windows 专用脚本保留 CRLF
# 解决 Windows IDE 把源码存成 CRLF、HEAD 是 LF 导致整文件行尾 diff 污染的问题
* text=auto eol=lf

# Windows 脚本(必须 CRLF 才能正确执行)
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf

# 二进制文件(不做行尾转换)
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.tgz binary
